Notes
-----

This LICENSE accompanies the bundled CSV in this directory
(`gov-orgs-en-ja.csv`) shipped with translation-toolkit v0.1.0, which was
extracted from the upstream PDF using `pdftotext -layout` plus heuristic
column splitting. The bundled CSV is approximately 3,000 entries —
representative coverage of ministries, agencies, bureaus, and positions.
